<br />

<br />
I have finally respecced Rob's RAs for PvE. Rob will NOT be returning to RvR. Not even for Relic raids. Mythic has sucked ALL the fun out of RvRing with Rob, and I will no longer throw him at the walls Mythic builds in front of him.
<br />

<br />
The lack of Mythic's response to the flaws in their system AND game has finally gotten through to me. Damage rules RvR. Other things used to couner that. Mythic has been removing those counters. Make a damage dealer, and enjoy RvR the Mythic way. You'll be much happier.
